{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441410/extras/Hand_Intro.gif?t=1738075445\" /><br><br>Drawing hands and feet are one of the hardest things to tackle in art. With HAELE 3D - Hand Poser you will have the perfect hand reference ready any time. It comes with many built in poses and preset scenes, but if you need something very specific you can create your own custom hand poses with one or two hands, pick male or female models, customize the material, environment and lighting to create your reference as you need it.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441410/extras/Posing.gif?t=1738075445\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441410/extras/Lights.gif?t=1738075445\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441410/extras/Environment.gif?t=1738075445\" /><br><br>Features: <br>- Female and male hands<br>- Preset poses<br>- Custom posing<br>- Editable lights: 3 Point light (color, intensity transformation), Environment light (HDRI map, intensity), Ground light (color, intensity) <br>- Environment: HDRI studio backgrounds, various environments, solid colors, <br>- Custom backgrounds<br>- Floor on/off, color, reflectivity<br>- Various skin tones<br>- Adjustable camera angle, location, position and field of view<br>- Save and load scenes<br>- Load presets<br><br>HAELE 3D - Hand Poses Pro is an easy to use anatomy and gesture drawing reference tool designed for beginner to advanced artists. With a diverse range of editable options, it serves as a resource for learning how to draw human hands. Whether your art style is realistic, stylized, cartoon, anime or anything in between, this is easy to use app complements tutorials and aids practicing your hand drawing or sculpting skills from sketch to finish.","back